<div id="DramaModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog">

        <!-- Modal content-->
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h4 class="modal-title">Drama Rules</h4>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>1. Registrations for Stage Play Competition are opened till 16th of November  </p><br />
                <p>2. Team should be consist of 4-7 only male participants.                      </p><br />
                <p>3. Maximum duration for play is 20 Minutes.                                   </p><br />
                <p>4. Performance, Morality, Content, Creativity and relevance with the topic will be judged. </p><br />
                <p>5. Music is strictly prohibited.                                              </p><br />
                <p>6. Upto Rs.80,000/- cash prize will be distributed among the winner team. </p><br />

            </div>

            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal" onclick="RulesAccepted()" id="RulesAccepted">Accept</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>


